WEBVTT

00:00.883 --> 00:02.719
<i>Nucky was like a son to me.</i>

00:02.754 --> 00:06.050
- But you're my flesh and blood, boy.
- So?

00:06.084 --> 00:09.340
So you're gonna take back
Atlantic City for the both of us.

00:09.375 --> 00:12.002
- We're all set for McGarrigle?
- My house Monday night.

00:12.037 --> 00:15.177
- <i>You're a credit to the cause, Nucky.</i>
- <i>Always happy to help.</i>

00:22.863 --> 00:25.260
You shot a white man
in the throat.

00:25.295 --> 00:27.293
I got four boys dead
in that warehouse.

00:27.327 --> 00:31.356
You do understand I'm the only
thing keeping you from a lynch mob?

00:31.391 --> 00:34.520
I can assure you that neither
I or sheriff Thompson

00:34.554 --> 00:36.720
will rest until these hooded cowards

00:36.754 --> 00:38.821
are brought to justice.

00:38.855 --> 00:40.822
These coloreds need
to learn a lesson,

00:40.856 --> 00:42.655
and we are going to teach it.

00:45.324 --> 00:47.323
Herman Dacus just died
from his neck wound.

00:47.358 --> 00:50.889
Find Chalky and place him
under arrest for his own safety.

00:50.924 --> 00:52.756
Will you stop worrying
for God's sake?

00:52.791 --> 00:54.257
I need to know
what's going on, Lou.

00:54.291 --> 00:56.790
Chalky's out of the game.
That's a pretty good start.

00:56.824 --> 01:00.026
<i>Got that whole warehouse</i>
<i>that's there for the taking.</i>

01:00.060 --> 01:01.491
I want you to meet
the governor,

01:01.526 --> 01:04.259
cultivate relationships;
New York, Philly.

01:04.293 --> 01:06.292
- What's this?
- From Nucky.

01:06.327 --> 01:08.726
<i>A wedding gift.</i>

01:08.760 --> 01:11.194
Yesterday morning at Chalky's,

01:11.228 --> 01:13.127
you saw nothing that
aroused your suspicion?

01:13.162 --> 01:16.461
It happened after we left.

01:16.496 --> 01:19.630
- What the hell is going on?
- My name is Solomon Bishop.

01:19.665 --> 01:21.464
<i>We're with the attorney</i>
<i>general's office.</i>

01:21.498 --> 01:23.132
You're under arrest
for election fraud.

